Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,独立第八部队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加把劲 奈美惠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修正 向右+3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准修正 向右+3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修正 -1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准修正 -1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准修正完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何 这新型枪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是专用枪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命中精度高 用起来也顺手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且银色歼灭者全面点检后状态极佳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在说可能不合适
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿些喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去快回啊 还有运行测试要做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是独立第八部队没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,错倒是没错{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是奈美惠{\rsymbol}·{\r}波特曼上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即日起正式加入独立第八部队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我是吉米{\rsymbol}·{\r}哈兹福特 平民技师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次被调任 有些紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 难不成 你是青蓝的机师?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我没多少实战经验
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道第八部队的各位愿不愿接受我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这部队没那么特别
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是精英部队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说是困难任务也能手到擒来的精英部队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就亲眼验证一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 要吃糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没啥 只是觉得你可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可可可可爱{\rsymbol}…{\r}我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我{\rsymbol}…{\r}我给你带路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有刮伤 光洁锃亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就满是划痕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最新型机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZTK5型 青蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,性能比黑耀和金刚高出一个档次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能跟银色歼灭者争高下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有这么强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于用了碳纳米薄膜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有往日一半的厚度 重量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能发挥原版装甲的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,功率也胜出一截哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,配最新机型来 是说上面认可咱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这意味着将来战场会更加严酷罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很值得整备一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说明书送来了没
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光简易说明书就三大箱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 那女孩是{\rsymbol}…{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新来的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是奈美惠{\rsymbol}·{\r}波特曼上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即日起 正式加入第八部队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后 这边几位是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我是奈美惠{\rsymbol}·{\r}波特曼上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即日起{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有男友没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 喜欢什么类型?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有恋人没?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年长点的?年少点的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有搭档没?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃{\rsymbol}…{\r}吃糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有测试要弄{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为来了新机师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗学长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长 没想到会在这里见到学长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新来的机师 原来是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你驾驶没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个不要提啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是奈美惠{\rsymbol}·{\r}波特曼上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即日起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,@%#*#&@*%#￥@
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肿{\rsymbol}…{\r}肿么了{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脸有点红
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又给人糖了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们认识?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机动兵器运用科的学妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然学年不同 但很合得来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合得来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长 队长在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长在那边那辆{\rsymbol}…{\r}指挥车里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 能陪我去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米小姐 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这好吗 放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:08:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真坚强 能装出一脸没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竞争者登场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么竞争者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们永远 都是支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长这会儿不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就回来了 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在旧机型难以应付的不稳定地形上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青蓝可以迅速自动修正姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:09:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只专注开枪就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个范本资料中的人物简介{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是机动作战的参考模特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 笑脸不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看又没啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这张照片本该删掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勅使河原重工可是兵工厂的龙头老大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们拿你的资料为基准
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很优秀嘛 奈美惠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 哪里的话{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后就看实战时 能做多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是劳伦斯 没发现敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劳伦斯机 被击毁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波特曼上等兵 很优秀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不简单嘛 奈美惠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按青蓝的性能 这在预想之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要保持下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被妹子打倒也不坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 也不该被干掉两次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有第三次 就说不过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各机 请移动至下一演习地点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,状态不错啊 时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进上等兵 你太冲前了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 奈美惠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我也有错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不习惯有部下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是埋怨我给你配了搭档?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝无此事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 奈美惠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人从左侧接近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右侧可是山丘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有高低差 被盯上很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那对面是陡坡 青蓝应该爬不上来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真爬不上来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波特曼上等兵 被击毁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来泉那家伙 是想让这幼狮出来见见世面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通过实战锻炼她 看来是我们的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿普尔顿军曹做得很精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱利亚诺伍长战死两次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《劳伦斯{\rsymbol}·{\r}朱利亚诺之{\fsp0}You Only Live Twice{\r}》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三战两胜 很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽想如此说 但战斗中问题百出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于熟知青蓝性能 波特曼上等兵的意见值得尊重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如何活用 要由你这小队长判断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战场上判断失误 等于宣告死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庆幸这只是模拟战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错 是我{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各自 分析今天的模拟战 上交报告书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我居然蠢到认为自己对青蓝了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它竟能爬那种陡坡{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠 副队长说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何活用部下的意见要由我判断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 学长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗 最近的同步率真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是跟银歼关系越来越深了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回头 漫不经心地表扬他一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漫不经心啦 漫不经心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,省得他骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 你没来开会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 整理数据花了点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是 时宗 你们关系进展很顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,联系不是挺紧密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样哪算好关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本没什么紧密联系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对方的想法 得了如指掌才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 要像手脚一样随便用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 这说法太过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 就算不用一心同体 也得有相当的信赖关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力完成这目标吧 咱们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说 奈美惠的事和吉米没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是银歼啊可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很差劲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手册上没写的事 我就对付不来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按手册来的战斗 首先就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最初肩膀中弹虽然愣神了 但那损伤仍能做躲避动作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这样 真能参加实战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说出来不怕笑话 紧张感完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实弹很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然可怕 为什么还要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为驾驶着银色歼灭者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.77,0:15:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,操纵时心情很舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉自己无所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机体就像身体的延长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我{\rsymbol}…{\r}开青蓝能到那境界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算想着有青蓝保护 也很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怕不要紧 战斗时不是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有同伴在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会多加训练 让自己足以支援学长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 还有五公里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那丫头不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说模拟战犯错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是常有人说吗 战场让士兵成长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}最近都闲死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说这种话 会被上头叫去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧急集合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让波特曼上等兵参与实战太危险了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地点 α-12-Z
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有移动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠 你清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次负责后方支援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 超过50%
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有按手册来的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确认敌方部队撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作战结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也开始撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很短暂 但联动深度超过了70%?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有学长 我现在已经{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你也做到了临机应变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是托学长的福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要继续积累经验 就能更加应对自如
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的不错嘛 学长君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救下奈美惠 我终于懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我至今为止 一直在几位的支援下战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真迟钝啊 时宗君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 明白了这件事 就没白多个部下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要继续积累经验 就能更加应对自如
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请{\rsymbol}…{\r}请别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.14,0:21:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 这句会成经典台词哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干啥 我可是在夸你 是吧军曹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有在夸 根本是逗我玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 从你嘴里居然能说出这么有理的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变得很可靠了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 下次我听时宗学长指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,500)\bord3\be1\fs60\fad(500,0)}亡灵
